                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-108-off571 t18020428-108-cd572"></join>, a silver watch, value 15s. a gold chain, value 10s. and a gold seal, value 10s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18020428-108-victim783" type="victimName">
                        Joseph 
                        Hall
                     <interp inst="t18020428-108-victim783" type="surname" value="Hall"></interp>
